snippet.title: Sonic Battle R Sage 2024 Update Trailer
snippet.description:
I'm back and on the Sonic Battle R development team. Here to show yall what we cooked for this update. More stages will have night time, more cosmetics will be available, and of course more stages to race on. I'll see you guys on the track!

Discord link to join: https://discord.gg/cefUfnuMFN
